<div class="form-container">
    <h2>CONTACT</h2>
    <p class="reach-out">I'm always interested in hearing from anyone who visits this site.  Please don't hesitate to reach out to me for any reason.  I'm always open to taking on new projects, or helping a fellow developer.  Drop me a line below, and I'll respond as soon as I can!</p>
    {{msg}}
    <form method="POST" action="send">
        <p>
            <label for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="name">
        </p>
        <p>
            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" name="email">
        </p>
        <p>
            <label for="message">Message</label>
            <textarea name="message" rows="5"></textarea>
        </p>
        <p>
            <button type="submit">SUBMIT</button>
        </p>
    </form>
</div>